>>21477529

It takes a while to get it to work. If you want good results, you're going to have to put some effort in. Some people, they can have their first lucid dream in a week. Others, it might take months.

Anyway, you shouldn't believe anything you read on 4chan without looking shit up on a more reputable site, so look up a guy called Tim Post. He runs a lucid dreaming forum with a lot of good resources. Can't miss him, he looks like Keanu Reeves but with a buzz cut.
The other guy to look up would be Stephen LaBerge. He's got a Ph.D from Stanford in Psychophysiology and wrote an informative book on the subject called "Exploring the World of Lucid Dreaming".
